      x Divine Regeneration (targets others)
      x Hellfire spell
      x Electric Hellfire
      x Dispelling bolt
      x Abjure earth demon (anti-revgenunkim). Irresist damage; effects:
        x Loss of claw/innate attacks ("X's claw explodes into gore!")
        x Loss of rArmor and rAcid ("X's skin blisters horribly!")
        x Negative rArmor ("X's flesh melts and sloughs off!")
        x Fear status ("X shudders in primal terror!", "X is overcome by the fear of death!")
        x Paralysis (2-4 turns) ("X's devouring spirit is momentarily torn from its body!")
        x Loss of mobility ("X's bones shatter, and it writhes in agony!")
        x Instant death, 10% chance ("X's head explodes into gore!!")
        x HP is cut in half if HP > 1 ("X convulses in torment!")
      x Rolling boulder
        x Flying status
          x Apply to mellaents, spectral swords, stalkers
      x Frozen fiend living ice ability (basalt themed, like basalt fiend)
      x Speeding bolt (more damage per distance)
    x Stats
      x Martial, Spikes/riposte
      x Slow, decreased melee+missile, decreased evade (negative power rating)
    x Spell descriptions
