*** 4.1.0 release ***
- Night creatures, part two
  - More "ethereal" feel
    - Slade
      - Indestructible by any means
      x When standing on it, nothing outside lair can be seen (player-only?)
      x When not on it, vision into lair is sharply decreased
      x Color dance (walls also)
    - Door should be invisible unless adjacent (or positive NC rep)
  x Night shard: negative light
  x Spectral Flan: gurgling creature that paralyses player, then touches player
    to teleport them outside of lair
    - Rebuilds door?
      - Teleportation erases memory of the lair?
      - "Scrambles" the inside?
  - Balance conjuration
    - Conjuration ring prefab (both lair and Prison) should have heavy guards
      - Prison one should be larger so that it's harder to accidentally aggro them
    - Conjuration ring prefab should be rarer
    - Spectral orbs rarer
    x More non-ring conjuration items
      x Spectral Eye: consumable, create a region of slade in a dark area
        x Spectral Tyrant: immobile, extremely fast
          x Dreaming Mind spell (1 turn of insanity, 0 MP)
          x Also Conjuration spell (10 MP)
            - Conjuration stat is mirror of player's (but no conjuration augments)
          x Blades and Tyrant are aligned with the Night
      x Spectral Wisp: throwing it spawns spectral blades in that location.
- Additional mundane items and content
  - New polearm: push ego
  - Mace/morningstar: stun/daze: unable to attack (also: add to debilitated).
- Save files
  x Memory leak fixes, refactoring
  - Automatic testing
  - Menu option to load a saved game
  - Escape-menu option to save a game
  - Anti-cheat?
  - Serialize the player's "surroundings" and context to show on main menu when
    loading a save
- Scoresheets
  x Website, highscore page
  - Record surroundings in more meaningful way
  - Adding an actual score
    - Record version of game, use different scoring methods for different versions
    - Record number of times player was spotted (ignore statues)
- UI/QoL
  - Escape menu
    - List of visited/unvisited floors
  - Examine mode
    - Fix: clicking area of map doesn't start examine mode on correct coord
    x Ability to view info on gas/terrain/wall/floor
    - Effect lists
      x Gas: clicking on gas to see popup window with stats
      - Status: clicking on status (e.g. potion screen doesn't have this)
  - If mob is shouting, blink sound symbol
  - If mob is making noise, sound symbol in HUD
  x Effects of iron wasp attacks not shown for some reason
  x Throwing/Choosing coordinate
    x Rework/Fix UI that shows area size of potion being thrown
    x Show area of effect for distraction potion when throwing
  - Message when unable to push past ally
x Balancing of early game
  x Make it a little harder to be stocked up on armor in the beginning
  x Cloaks should be rarer
- More rings
  - Ring of refrigeration
  - Ring of revelation
  - Ring of suggestion
  - Ring of contriction
  - Ring of excavation
  - Ring of execution
- Fire tweaks
  - Don't destroy corpses entirely, only char them
  - Monsters should scream when on fire, and do fireWork() (i.e. run around and panic)
  - Smoke when burning things
- Add traps back in, reworking them to be useful
  - Idea: Vents are always near doors?
- Events
  - Lore quick speeches/monologues
  - Workshop/2 and Workshop/3
    - enh. Emberling, enh. Emberling event
  - Crypt
    - Ambassador
    x Revgen (see notes in green notebook)
